{"id": 1963, "genre": 1001, "title": "你在年轻人身上见过哪些中年气息？", "description": "那些在气质上未老先衰的画面都是怎样的？", "record_count": 6835, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171018103146zblTpG1Um9DYRBAt.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-10-19T03:00:49Z", "options": [{"id": 242688, "content": "带奢侈品来暗示地位和收入", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 297241}, {"id": 242944, "content": "喜欢盘核桃...", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1144513}, {"id": 243200, "content": "还没有开始奋斗就考虑如何养老了……", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1163807}, {"id": 242689, "content": "每天做饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 878308}, {"id": 242690, "content": "失去了对新鲜事物的好奇心", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 79304}, {"id": 242691, "content": "开始不再关注明星资讯（和一些新鲜出炉的新“星”）", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 79304}, {"id": 242947, "content": "热水瓶", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1157825}, {"id": 242692, "content": "啤酒肚 穿秋裤", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1157740}, {"id": 242948, "content": "ktv一上来就是李宗盛的《山丘》", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1038029}, {"id": 242693, "content": "室友天天在寝室看红歌会…老x讲故事…一类的我爸妈都不看只有我爷爷奶奶扣手机的时候的背景音节目…", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 570334}, {"id": 242949, "content": "喜欢回忆", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1024309}, {"id": 242694, "content": "抬头纹", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1151273}, {"id": 242950, "content": "上学", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1161483}, {"id": 242695, "content": "少白头", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1062101}, {"id": 242951, "content": "吐槽关注代表大会的，是是是，你不用考试你牛掰", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1080074}, {"id": 242952, "content": "开始渴望安稳，没有冲劲！", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1161492}, {"id": 243208, "content": "早上起来要喝热水，上火不能吃辣", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 849659}, {"id": 242697, "content": "我这个老年人啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1153777}, {"id": 242953, "content": "玉配饰，古玩，干部西服，保温杯。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1161493}, {"id": 242698, "content": "饮食开始偏好清淡一点的", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1159736}, {"id": 242954, "content": "不运动", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 945706}, {"id": 243466, "content": "掉头发", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 763208}, {"id": 242699, "content": "来回答这个问题。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1159745}, {"id": 242955, "content": "“现在这些偶像/产品/创意（and so on）比我们那时候的xx差远了”", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1141979}, {"id": 242700, "content": "越来越喜欢说 过几年 你就明白了 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1159736}, {"id": 242956, "content": "拒绝改变，拒绝冒险", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147506}, {"id": 242701, "content": "看太开", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1018954}, {"id": 242957, "content": "试水", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1115653}, {"id": 242702, "content": "枸杞泡茶，“你们这群年轻人啊……”", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1159769}, {"id": 242958, "content": "风险转移的职场法则", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 785